### Hadith 1:749

*Narrated Abu Huraira:*

Allah's Apostle said, "Say Amen' when the Imam says "Ghair-il-maghdubi
'alaihim wala-ddal-lin; not the path of those who earn Your Anger (such
as Jews) nor of those who go astray (such as Christians); all the past
sins of the person whose saying (of Amin) coincides with that of the
angels, will be forgiven.

